Miscellaneous Highlights: The Pakistan T20I squad will play 3-match T20I series against Ireland at home in Dublin.
The Ireland T20I squad will also play the 3-match T20I series against Pakistan in Dublin.
Others: The first match of the series will begin on May 10 at the Clontarf Cricket Club in Dublin.
The Pakistan vs Ireland T20 series will be live streamed on Fancode app, but it is not free as the user have to give Rs 69 to purchase their tour pass subscription.
